longBusinessSummary: Adventure Box Technology AB (publ) operates as a computer game technology company in Sweden. It operates KoGaMa, a social cloud platform that allows users to create, share, and play 3D computer games online; and provides licensing and consulting services. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
